WebLogic Server 9.1 now fully supports the Java 2 Enterprise Edition (J2EE) 1.4 specification including support for the following J2EE APIs:

    * J2EE 1.4, including:
          o Enterprise JavaBeans (EJB) 2.1
          o Servlet 2.4
          o Java ServerPages (JSP) 2.0
          o Java Database Connectivity (JDBC) 3.0
          o Java Connector Architecture (JCA) 1.5
          o Java Messaging Service (JMS) 1.1
          o Java Management Extensions (JMX) 1.2
    * Struts
    * Beehive (Apache)
    * Spring
    * JSR-181 (Web Services)